summary.span: 表示将 ASP.NET 跟踪事件路由到 IIS 7.0 基础结构的事件提供程序。

span.span: Represents an event provider that routes ASP.NET tracing events to the IIS 7.0 infrastructure.

remarks.format: ## Remarks ASP.NET 运行状况监视，管理员可管理已部署 Web 应用程序。ASP.NET health monitoring enables administrators to manage deployed Web applications. 命名空间包含的事件类型可获取运行状况状态数据和处理此数据提供程序类型。The namespace contains the event types that obtain health-status data and the provider types that process this data. 它还包含支持类型，可帮助你管理运行状况事件。It also contains supporting types that help you manage health events. 类是通过路由是通过处理 ASP.NET 跟踪事件的自定义的运行状况事件提供程序[!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)]跟踪基础结构。The class is a customized health-event provider that processes ASP.NET tracing events by routing them through the [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] tracing infrastructure. 此路由会发生仅跟踪启用 ASP.NET 中。This routing occurs only when tracing is enabled in ASP.NET. 中引入[!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)]。 is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)]. 有关详细信息，请参见[版本和依赖关系](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md)。For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md). > [!NOTE] > 此类不路由[!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)]asp.net 跟踪事件页上的事件。This class does not route [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] trace events into ASP.NET page events.

summary.span: 将事件从提供程序缓冲区移到事件日志中。

span.span: Moves the events from the provider's buffer into the event log.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 调用此方法时，缓冲区中的所有事件会立即从缓冲区都移到事件日志。When this method is called, all the events in the buffer are immediately moved from the buffer to the event log. 而不考虑的最后一个事件编写后经过多长时间或缓冲区中有多少个事件都发生这种情况。This occurs regardless of how much time has elapsed since the last event was written or how many events are in the buffer. 上次写入事件的时间将重置为刷新操作的时间。The time of the last written event is reset to the time of the flushing action. 中引入[!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)]。 is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)]. 有关详细信息，请参见[版本和依赖关系](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md)。For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
